.row
  .col-sm-6
    .form-group(ng-class="{ 'has-error': vm.hasFieldError(form.type) }")
      label Type
      input.form-control(
        type="text"
        name="type"
        ng-model="telephoneNumber.medium.type"
        required
        ng-maxlength="30"
      )
      .help-block(
        ng-messages="form.type.$error"
        ng-show="vm.hasFieldError(form.type)"
      )
        span(ng-message="required") 必填字段
        span(ng-message="maxlength") 字段不能超过 30 个字符.
  .col-sm-6
    .form-group(ng-class="{ 'has-error': vm.hasFieldError(form.number) }")
      label Number
      input.form-control(
        international-phone-number,
        type="text"
        name="number"
        ng-model="telephoneNumber.medium.number",
        convert-to-phone-number,
        required
      )
      .help-block(
        ng-messages="form.number.$error"
        ng-show="vm.hasFieldError(form.number)"
      )
        span(ng-message="required") 必填字段
        span(ng-message="internationalPhoneNumber") 字段必须是合法的数字.